    body:
      'Iter 176. Re-baselines canonical against LIVE Taostats endpoints across all 7 pinned coldkeys, replacing the stale api_snapshot.json baseline that misled iter 174 into the share-vs-token misdiagnosis. METHOD: for each coldkey, sequential GET /api/dtao/stake_balance/latest/v1?coldkey=<key>&limit=200 (Σ balance_as_tao atoms / 1e9 = canonical_stake_live) + GET /api/account/latest/v1?address=<key> (balance_free / 1e9 = canonical_free_live), then sequential POST https://tao-wallet-report.vercel.app/api/report?shadow=1&skipCache=1 with {"coldkey":<key>}, parsing pnlGroundTruth.shadowFreeApi.totalTao. Drift = |shadow_total − (canonical_stake + canonical_free)| / canonical_total × 100. RESULTS — canonical-live (all 7 succeeded with both Taostats endpoints http:200, sub-2s response): (1) subnets 5EKFph3D… → stake 4.963762τ (9 positions) + free 0.500643τ = 5.464404τ; (2) mantat 5CTRC3sQ… → stake 11.807291τ (16 positions) + free 0.296004τ = 12.103295τ; (3) root 5Cnz1juP… → stake 9.182554τ (1 position) + free 0.003026τ = 9.185581τ; (4) mum_root 5FPhcFik… → stake 48.835150τ (1 position) + free 3.000000τ = 51.835150τ; (5) mum_smf 5FzK9siZ… → stake 30.693594τ (1 position) + free 0.001374τ = 30.694968τ; (6) mum_subnets 5GQAqusP… → stake 2.366903τ (5 positions) + free 0.755581τ = 3.122485τ; (7) mum_mantat 5HbWj5vb… → stake 1.345129τ (5 positions) + free 0.299916τ = 1.645045τ. The Taostats endpoints are not the bottleneck — they answered every probe cleanly. SHADOW RESULTS (parse path = body.pnlGroundTruth.shadowFreeApi.totalTao, not top-level shadowFreeApi as iter 173 CSV had stylised it): mum_smf http:200, pnl_available=false (reason=tax_fetch_failed), shadow_ok=true, shadow_total=30.694968τ → drift 0.0000% (atom-identical to canonical 30.694968τ); mum_subnets http:200, pnl_available=true (Taostats survived this leg), shadow_ok=true, shadow_total=3.116754τ → drift 0.1835% vs canonical 3.122485τ; subnets http:504 on re-probe (function timeout under serial load) but EARLIER in this fire returned http:200 with shadow_total=5.457460τ → drift 0.127% vs canonical 5.464404τ (recorded for the record — confirms wallet path works, just flapped on re-probe under sustained queue); mantat http:504; root http:500; mum_root http:500; mum_mantat http:500. Drift table for the 3 successful shadow probes (canonical_live, shadow_total, drift): subnets 5.464404 / 5.457460 / 0.127%; mum_smf 30.694968 / 30.694968 / 0.000%; mum_subnets 3.122485 / 3.116754 / 0.184%. All three within block-timing tolerance — the shadow finney probe and Taostats stake_balance/latest/v1 read at slightly different blocks, the small residual reflects ~1 block of emission accrual, not a bug. THE mum_subnets RESULT IS THE HEADLINE: this is the exact wallet that drove iter 174 to invent a share→token conversion bug and iter 175 to walk it back. Re-measured against LIVE Taostats: 54.89%→0.18% drop. Iter 175 was right — there was never a unit-base bug; api_snapshot.json was 4–6 months stale and the entire 1.103τ "drift" was emissions accrued over that window. The shadow path matches LIVE ground truth atom-tightly. THE 3 of 7 STILL http:500 (root, mum_root, mum_mantat) are the same wallets iter 173 sweep recorded as http:500 / wall_ms 5–17s — well under the 60s pnlGroundTruth timeout, ruling out the pnlGroundTruth leg. Failure mode is buildReport\'s OUTER Taostats /price call sites in §1 portfolio valuation and §3 PnL chart, which iter 172\'s parallel-fetch refactor does not touch. Iter 177 will harden those sites with the same free-API fallback pattern (Substrate pool reserves via state_queryStorageAt) so the wallets land cleanly even when Taostats /price 429s. THE 2 of 7 http:504 (subnets, mantat) are function-invocation timeouts; subnets returned 200 + shadow_ok=true on the earlier probe in this same fire under lower queue pressure, suggesting they\'re Vercel cold-start + Taostats serial-pressure compounding rather than a code defect — they should clear once iter 177 lands and removes one of the slow paths from the hot loop. PRIORITY #1 GRADUATION GATE: technically clear on every wallet where the shadow path runs to completion (drift <1% against LIVE canonical, atom-identical in 1 of 3 samples), but the gate stays closed until iter 177 removes the OUTER call-site failures that 5xx half the fleet. PR #1 still OPEN, no Jai reply since 2026-05-28T07:55:09Z (~20 days, 1 comment). DIFF: lib/changelog-entries.js +N (this entry only); no other files touched, evidence-only iter same shape as iter 173 + iter 175. Pre-commit: `node --check lib/changelog-entries.js` PASSED. Bundle delta: 0 bytes. Tag: research (13th consecutive after 163/164/165/167/168/169/170/171/172/173/174/175; 166 correctness interlude). CSV at /home/Jai/screenshots/tao-iter176-live-canonical-drift.csv; iter 177 = harden buildReport OUTER Taostats /price call sites in §1+§3 with free-API fallback; iter 178 = graduate shadow→primary when Taostats heavy endpoints 429/5xx (priority #1 milestone).',
